Package ohos.aafwk.ability

Class DataAbilityOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.aafwk.ability.DataAbilityOperation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class DataAbilityOperation
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Performs an operation on the database.

    DataAbilityOperation describes a single operation among a batch of operations that can be performed on the database, such as add, delete, update, or query.

    Since:
    1
